        <div>
          <h2 id="brushes">Brushes</h2>
            <img src="C:\Users\Mike\Documents\Projects\Dasmoto's Arts and Crafts\Resources\brushes1.webp">
          <h3>Hacksaw Brushes</h3>
            <p>Made of the highest quality oak, Hacksaw brushes are known for their weight and ability to hold paint in large amounts.</p>
            <p>Available in differnt sizes.</p>
            <p id="bold">Starting at $3.00 / brush.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 id="frames">Frames</h2>
            <img src="C:\Users\Mike\Documents\Projects\Dasmoto's Arts and Crafts\Resources\frames1.webp">
          <h3>Art Frames (assorted)</h3>
            <p>Assorted frames made of different material, including MDF, Birchwood, and PDE. Select frames can be sanded and painted according to your needs.</p>
            <p id="bold">Starting at $2.00 / frame.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 id="paint">Paint</h2>
            <img src="C:\Users\Mike\Documents\Projects\Dasmoto's Arts and Crafts\Resources\paint1.webp">
          <h3>Clean Finnish Paint</h3>
            <p>Imported paint from Finland. Over 256 colors available in-store, varying in quantity (1 oz. to 8 oz.) Clean Finnish paint microbinds to canvas, increasing the finish and longevity of any artwork.</p>
            <p id="bold"> Starting at $5.00 / tube.</p>  
        </div>
